# React patterns

- Mark client components with `'use client'` only when they use hooks, browser APIs, or event handlers.
- Keep pages as Server Components when possible; push interactivity into feature components.
- Use TanStack Query for server/async data; use Zustand for client UI state.
- Co-locate feature state in `<feature>.store.ts` next to the feature component.
- Extract subcomponents only when it improves readability and keeps files under 100 lines.
